                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6252" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0113</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7912 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">同心助力碳中和，齐头并进共发展——佛燃能源的社会责任实践之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Work Together to Help Carbon Neutrality, Go Hand in Hand  and Develop Together: Foran Energy&#39;s Social Responsibility Practice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">彭中文，危唯，郭若玉，梁志方，蒲雨琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佛燃能源集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佛燃能源；企业社会责任；企业价值；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Foran Energy; corporate social responsibility; corporate value; stakeholder theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">现阶段国家针对全球气候变暖提出有关碳中和的承诺，要求我国企业积极履行其自身的社会责任，共同应对全球气候变暖，而在碳中和方面能源行业的表现显得尤为重要。佛燃能源创立于1992年，是广东省乃至华南地区颇具实力的综合能源企业。佛燃能源以“汇聚清洁能源、共创美好明天”为使命，致力成为优秀的中国能源服务商。在履行社会责任的过程中，佛燃能源通过一系列的决策和实践，注重各利益相关方的期望和要求，并建立常态化的沟通和交流机制，通过多途径、多层次、多形式的沟通交流活动，在各方反馈的基础上不断完善和改进，并最终在履行社会责任的过程中取得了一些成就。本案例旨在为我国企业在履行社会责任过程中提供指导与实践参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At this stage, countries have made carbon neutral commitments in response to global warming, requiring Chinese companies to actively fulfill their own social responsibilities and jointly respond to global warming. The performance of the energy industry in terms of carbon neutrality is particularly important. Founded in 1992, Foran Energy is a powerful comprehensive energy company in Guangdong Province and even southern China. With the mission of “Gathering clean energy and creating a better tomorrow”, Foran Energy is committed to becoming an excellent Chinese energy service provider. In the process of fulfilling its social responsibilities, Foran Energy pays attention to the expectations and requirements of various stakeholders through a series of decisions and practices, and establishes a normalized communication and exchange mechanism through multi-channel, multi-level, and multi-form communication activities have been continuously improved and improved on the basis of feedback from all parties, and finally achieved some achievements in the process of fulfilling social responsibilities. This case aims to provide guidance and practical reference for Chinese enterprises in the process of fulfilling their social responsibilities. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会伦理》、《战略管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业管理与企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-04</td>
